article.description: — DeVante' Jones had 30 points as Coastal Carolina defeated Troy 90-81 on Friday night.
article.headline: Jones scores 30 to lead Coastal Carolina over Troy 90-81
article.linkText: Jones scores 30 to lead Coastal Carolina over Troy 90-81
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — DeVante' Jones had 30 points as Coastal Carolina defeated Troy 90-81 on Friday night. Jones hit 9 of 11 shots. He added eight rebounds and six assists. Tyrik Dixon had 12 points for Coastal Carolina (10-3, 4-2 Sun Belt Conference). Kevin Williamson and Ahmard Harvey each had 10 points. Kam Woods had 21 points for the Trojans (6-8, 1-4), whose losing streak reached four games. Zay Williams added 16 points and 12 rebounds and Kieffer Punter had 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
